iscount (>=2 years) applies 20% off the policy base premium\");\n33\t  it.todo(\"exactly 2 years customer receives loyalty discount\");\n34\t  it.todo(\"follow-up contract (second quote in scenario) applies 15% discount\");\n35\t  it.todo(\"first-insurance surcharge applies per item even for follow-up contracts\");\n36\t\n37\t  // Multi-item modifier scope\n38\t  it.todo(\"cursed surcharge applies only to cursed item, not whole policy\");\n39\t\n40\t  // Rounding\n41\t  it.todo(\"premium rounds up in MHPCO's favor\");\n42\t\n43\t  // Integration examples\n44\t  it.todo(\"newcomer with cursed sword: 165 G\");\n45\t  it.todo(\"long-standing customer's second contract with cursed enchantment-7 sword: 160 G\");\n46\t\n47\t  // Claim: basic payouts\n48\t  it.todo(\"regular sword damage 500 G yields payout 400 G (minus 100 deductible)\");\n49\t  it.todo(\"damage to rune (250 G value) of 200 G yields payout 100 G\");\n50\t  it.todo(\"high-enchantment (>=8) item: 50% reimbursement then deductible\");\n51\t  it.todo(\"dragon material item: full reimbursement then deductible\");\n52\t  it.todo(\"dragon material with enchantment 9: 50% wins, then deductible\");\n53\t\n54\t  // Claim: cap and deductible\n55\t  it.todo(\"payout capped at 2x insurance sum across multiple claims\");\n56\t  it.todo(\"deductible applies per damaged item entry\");\n57\t  it.todo(\"two-sword policy: insurance sum 2000, cap 4000\");\n58\t  it.todo(\"payout rounds down in MHPCO's favor\");\n59\t\n60\t  // Errors\n61\t  it.todo(\"quote with unknown item type causes non-zero exit\");\n62\t  it.todo(\"claim against item not in policy causes non-zero exit\");\n63\t  it.todo(\"claim with negative damage amount causes non-zero exit\");\n64\t  it.todo(\"more damages of a type than insured items causes non-zero exit\");\n65\t\n66\t  // CLI\n67\t  it.todo(\"CLI reads JSON from stdin and writes results JSON to stdout\");\n68\t});\n69\t"}]},"uuid":"06d6fe8e-318a-4f78-b086-7f4327405d89","timestamp":"2026-05-16T22:3